==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Willingly
<hw>Will"ing*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a willing manner; with
free will; without reluctance; cheerfully.</def>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The condition of that people is not so much to be envied as some
would <qex>willingly</qex> represent it.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Willingness</ent>⟦br⟧
